      <description>&lt;p&gt;更新sqlsrv驱动后，产生TLS加密的问题，问题如下：&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-SQL&#34; data-lang=&#34;SQL&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;SQLSTATE&lt;/span&gt;[&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;08001&lt;/span&gt;]: [Microsoft][ODBC Driver &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;18&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;SQL&lt;/span&gt; Server]SSL Provider: [error:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1416&lt;/span&gt;F086:SSL routines:tls_process_server_certificate:certificate verify failed:&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;self&lt;/span&gt; signed certificate] &#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
